  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "{circled:\"78\"}\n\nDoesn't UBIK appear in trash (humble) form again and again, and only at the end does it disclose its true, divine nature? Like the Girl.\n\nValis (the magician) simulated my highest, most lofty concept of Real reality: like UBIK in full epiphany. Deprived of its usual mask -- tricked into putting on another (Acts) -- it then \"reveals itself\" -- it puts on the UBIK mask. --- AI voice: \"I am like the forest bird in \"Siegfried.\" ie a dove. The dove. And \"I am the commercial -- compare",
      "matched_alias": "Bill",
